        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对呀，今天素材池有点羞涩，只有一条特别炸的料，但我觉得这一个故事就够咱们唠一整期了。",
      "start": 12.787,
      "duration": 10.58,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_003_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_003_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哦？说来听听。",
      "start": 23.82,
      "duration": 1.306,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_004_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_004_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "博文你玩魔兽世界吗？就那个艾泽拉斯大陆。",
      "start": 25.531,
      "duration": 3.048,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_005_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_005_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "嗯，早年玩过，怀旧服也体验过。",
      "start": 29.012,
      "duration": 2.873,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_006_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_006_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "那你想象一下，有人搞了1800个DeepSeek的实例，浩浩荡荡跑进艾泽拉斯去\"保卫世界\"了，每个月成本才340块人民币。你敢信吗？",
      "start": 32.35,
      "duration": 12.321,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_007_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_007_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哈哈，这消息我看到了。这事儿乍一听很搞笑，但背后其实是个挺硬核的工程问题。",
      "start": 45.133,
      "duration": 6.313,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_008_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_008_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对吧！我就说嘛，这不可能是简单堆数量。你赶紧给听众翻译翻译，1800个实例到底是怎么个玩法？",
      "start": 51.897,
      "duration": 8.751,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_009_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_009_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "你看啊，DeepSeek的单次推理成本现在已经压到了非常低的水平，尤其是批量调用走API的话，单个实例的token费用可以忽略不计。但魔兽世界里角色操作是需要实时决策的——打哪个怪、走哪条路、什么时候吃药——所以每一个\"AI玩家\"其实都是一个独立的智能体。",
      "start": 61.148,
      "duration": 22.093,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_010_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_010_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哦我懂了，就是每个AI小号都有自己的\"大脑\"？",
      "start": 83.679,
      "duration": 3.657,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_011_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_011_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "没错，1800个大脑同时在线。算下来每个月的云端算力开销，加上网络带宽、存储日志那些杂费，340块人民币真的不是夸张。这放到两年前，想都不敢想。",
      "start": 87.797,
      "duration": 13.801,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_012_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_012_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "天哪，那这就是说以前那种动辄几万的游戏AI成本，现在直接被打到地板价了？",
      "start": 102.043,
      "duration": 7.706,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_013_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_013_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "可以这么理解。而且这个案例有意思的地方在于，它不是为了\"卷\"性能，而是验证了一个新的范式——小模型、大规模、协同作战。每个DeepSeek实例可能只负责一小片区域的任务，合起来却能覆盖整个服务器生态。",
      "start": 110.223,
      "duration": 17.042,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_014_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_014_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "我产品经理的直觉告诉我，这事儿远比打游戏值钱。博文你觉得呢？",
      "start": 127.692,
      "duration": 6.182,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_015_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_015_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "你说得太对了。这种\"廉价智能体集群\"的思路一旦成熟，从游戏代练到工业自动化、从客服中心到内容审核，全都会受益。艾泽拉斯只是一个开始，背后的方法论才是真正的价值。",
      "start": 134.338,
      "duration": 14.977,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_016_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_016_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "好家伙，一个魔兽故事聊出了工业革命的感觉。那咱们今天就以这个案例收尾吧——AI不再高高在上，它已经钻进游戏里，帮咱们\"保卫世界\"了。",
      "start": 149.732,
